<body>
  {{>header}}
  <div class="card">
    <p>Hello there! Welcome to my weather app!
      <br /><br />
      This weather app allows you to retrieve weather information such as temperature, wind
      speed, humidity etc, from any location you search from.

      It makes use of the <b>mapbox API</b> to retrieve geographical coordinates and then retrieve the weather
      information
      through the <b>weatherstack API</b>.
    </p>
    This is built with:
    <ul>
      <li>Node.js</li>
      <li>Express.js, to create web server</li>
      <li>Handlebars.js / hbs, as templating engine to render dynamic documents and create partials for reusability
      </li>
      <li>Postman-Request.js to facilitate asynchronous HTTP calls</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</body>

</html>